{"tid":1036281,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"又係我 搵冇貓愛心巴絲接收貓貓","createTime":"2019-02-25T06:25:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T02:23:05.000Z","uid":777,"like":39,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"3ad46dfa7f5cb6b1a48dcdcffec5e61eb2b66546","tid":1036281,"uid":777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T06:25:49.000Z","msg":"是咁的，詳情可以睇返我上個post都得<br />\n<br />\n經過差不多半年嘅時間<br />\n<br />\n貓貓同我家本來的貓貓夾唔到<br />\n<br />\n原因我估真係可能以後俾貓恰過令佢唔同其他貓玩<br />\n<br />\n我其實分開咗佢地<br />\n<br />\n只要有其他貓經過見到佢就即刻fee同行入去佢就會出手<br />\n<br />\n我放佢係屋企個細房仔到<br />\n<br />\n無奈其實空間唔多<br />\n<br />\n條友又唔會落地玩下 一日到黑就坐同訓<br />\n<br />\n佢越來越肥 我怕長久對佢隻腳唔好<br />\n<br />\n我試過放其他貓入房放佢出廳佢係驚到跑返轉頭<br />\n<br />\n貓仔性格其實真係好嗲人 個個都是肯痴<br />\n<br />\n我自己其實唔捨得 但唔想佢身體之後因爲冇走動而差<br />\n<br />\n想搵有興趣養貓嘅巴絲領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以tg我 <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Lunaandcats\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FLunaandcats&d=g2%2Fo6b0QjPi1xWtu1PcU8Ux5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=b4b0edbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Lunaandcats</a><br />\n<br />\n我要求好簡單 有窗網 本身冇貓（因為佢驚）<br />\n<br />\n錫貓愛貓 冇經驗可以大家研究<br />\n<br />\n貓仔醫生話1-2歲 係男仔 已絕育 性格親人好嗲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3rutQ4c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3rutQ4c.png&h=ac411803&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vokgZXB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvokgZXB.png&h=3f26309c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jet6CKi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjet6CKi.png&h=64682104&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/25/142418_2f1ab123ca13e72f738434607929a0ad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F25%2F142418_2f1ab123ca13e72f738434607929a0ad.png&h=fa816103&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/25/142421_1868abfbc9684552ecb9f3486e14b8aa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F25%2F142421_1868abfbc9684552ecb9f3486e14b8aa.png&h=0f7e950d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5dbc168e846f78231ae5bfc824e0baa59bda7d05","tid":1036281,"uid":18563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T06:42:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ecd2efd53e1cdfd95adace65a64976166d04469a","tid":1036281,"uid":238315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T06:55:09.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"4dbb75c52c0e53cb4f1575d47410098e4762a60b","tid":1036281,"uid":207968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T07:00:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d0d1c33e2f0e32ea6ff781782e0fcee58d3bfcd","tid":1036281,"uid":149563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T07:02:58.000Z","msg":"可惜我屋企有貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幫推"},{"pid":"44517f4ac1ea3311fbd62217315335c4fb25e567","tid":1036281,"uid":777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d0d1c33e2f0e32ea6ff781782e0fcee58d3bfcd","tid":1036281,"uid":149563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T07:02:58.000Z","msg":"可惜我屋企有貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幫推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T07:05:16.000Z","msg":"你隻貓幾大性格點？仔定女<br />\n其實我諗係因為我本身主子一開始太熱情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我隻野衝上去同佢玩佢以為打佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f776b266e9f5578eaea7262bf5cedb8fc6b537","tid":1036281,"uid":149563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44517f4ac1ea3311fbd62217315